n. it's not as fancy, but in my opinion it is an improvement when it comes to usability. maybe you can consider something similar for the stock owncloud theme. - also, to make this work, i had to rewrite parts of the files-app javascript files, not just the template. the javascript is a bit tightly coupled to the theme to allow the latter to be modified with more then just a bit of css.\r\n\r\ni haven't looked at a way to improve themeability yet. i just wanted to mention it now."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/30207236","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3340#issuecomment-30207236","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/3340","id":30207236,"user":{"login":"deepdiver1975","id":1005065,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/bdba071ed68da9ce8edae53c364902ef?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f67e101ad9531b7d25697b76e503e062e.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"bdba071ed68da9ce8edae53c364902ef","url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975","html_url":"https://github.com/deepdiver1975","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/deepdiver1975/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-12-10t08:27:18z","updated_at":"2013-12-10t08:27:18z","body":"@jancborchardt "},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/30213096","html_url":"https://github.com/owncl